                        strong
                            a(href='http://www.wuchao.info/webgis') Web GIS Information Service Platform
                        br
                        | 1. Designed and developed a full-stack Web GIS platform independently using a three-tier B/S architecture; implemented spatial data query, editing, and storage functionalities for interactive geographic information services.
                        br
                        | 2. Built a constrained path planning service leveraging PostgreSQL and pgRouting; optimized routing algorithms to support multi-condition navigation and efficient spatial computation.
                        br
                        | 3. Developed a 3D visualization demo of the Taohuayuan Scenic Area using CesiumJS; integrated terrain, building, and route data for immersive virtual geographic exploration.

                    p
                        strong
                            a(href='http://www.wuchao.info/data/SoftwareCup_SylixOS.mp4') The 11th “China Software Cup” College Student Software Design Competition
                        br
                        | 1. Developed a lightweight airport facial recognition system based on the domestic operating system SylixOS, leading high-level software design, defining the development roadmap, and breaking down tasks.
                        br
                        | 2. Trained facial recognition models under the PyTorch framework, including face detection, facial landmark detection, and feature vectorization, and completed framework conversion.
                        br
                        | 3. Implemented model inference in the NCNN framework and integrated core software functionalities into SylixOS, achieving over 90% facial recognition accuracy in official evaluations.

